promptUsed.user:
Please analyze these tweets from @cheeky-gorilla.eth and provide a summary of what they mainly talked about in the past week:

ETHDam III by @CryptoCanal is sure to be a highlight this year - love their focus on privacy and security!

You'll also be able to catch my talk on creating sustainable funding for Ethereum's core protocol development, aka @ProtocolGuild ⛓️🛡️

Join me May 9-11 in Amsterdam 🌷🇳🇱

Can't wait for @EthPrague this year, honored to be able to present @ProtocolGuild ⛓️🛡️

See you there in May 🫡

@alextnetto Waaay younger than I thought..! Happy birthday Alex 🫡

summary: The tweets from @cheeky-gorilla.eth mainly focus on upcoming events related to Ethereum, particularly the ETHDam III event by @CryptoCanal and @EthPrague. They also mention their talk on sustainable funding for Ethereum's core protocol development through @ProtocolGuild. The tone seems positive and enthusiastic about the events and opportunities to present at them. Additionally, there is a casual mention of wishing someone a happy birthday.
